  "steps": [
    "Boil sufficient water in a deep pan, add 1 tablespoon oil, salt and noodles. Cook for 6-8 minutes. Drain the noodles and put them in a strainer, pour chilled water, drizzle some oil and mix well. Set aside.",
    "Cut carrot into thin slices and further into strips. Shred cabbage thinly. Deseed and cut green capsicum into thin strips. Halve the onion and thinly slice it horizontally and separate the layers. Cut some spring onion greens diagonally into ½ inch pieces and chop the remaining greens finely.",
    "Heat 2 tablespoons oil in a non-stick wok, add garlic, ginger and green chillies, mix and sauté till golden brown.",
    "Add onion, carrot, cabbage and green capsicum, mix well and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add noodles, light soy sauce, white pepper powder, salt, stock cube powder and vinegar, toss well and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add chopped spring onion greens and mix well.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl, sprinkle diagonally sliced spring onion greens and serve hot."
